text: Abdurahman Nasser (Arabic:عبد الرحمن ناصر) (born 16 February 1991) is a Qatari footballer who played in the Qatar Stars League for Al Sadd. ==References== Category:Qatari footballers Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Al Sadd SC players Category:Muaither SC players Category:Qatari people of Yemeni descent Category:Qatar Stars League players Category:Qatari Second Division players Category:Association football defenders
